[{"location":"#OptimalBath","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath","text":"Documentation for OptimalBath.\n\n","category":"section"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.ForwardADGradient","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.ForwardADGradient","text":"ForwardADGradient(bathymetry::AbstractArray, β::AbstractArray)\n\nA gradient computation strategy using ForwardDiff for automatic differentiation. Stores two preallocated buffers: one for the bathymetry and one for the gradient results. The bathymetry starts as a copy of the initial bathymetry, and is updated during gradient computations.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"type"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.SinFVMPrimalSWEProblem","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.SinFVMPrimalSWEProblem","text":"SinFVMPrimalSWEProblem\n\nWrapper around SinFVM. Contains problem definition and solver parameters.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"type"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.compute_flux_source-NTuple{4, Any}","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.compute_flux_source","text":"compute_flux_source(Λ, Ul, Ur, Δx)\n\nComputes the source due to the reformulation of the adjoint pde to conservative form.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.compute_objective","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.compute_objective","text":"compute_objective(U, t, x, β, gradient_data::GradientData)\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.compute_objective_and_gradient","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.compute_objective_and_gradient","text":"compute_objective_and_gradient(β, primal_swe_problem::PrimalSWEProblem, data::GradientData, ::GradientType)\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.compute_objective_and_gradient!","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.compute_objective_and_gradient!","text":"compute_objective_and_gradient!(G, β, primal_swe_problem::PrimalSWEProblem, data::GradientData, gradient_type::GradientType)\n\nAssigns the gradient of the objective function with respect to the parameters β into G, and returns the objective function value.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.objective_density","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.objective_density","text":"objective_density(::Objective, U)\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.objective_density_gradient","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.objective_density_gradient","text":"objective_density_gradient(obj::Objective, U)\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.solve_primal","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.solve_primal","text":"solve_primal(primal_swe_problem::PrimalSWEProblem, bathymetry)\n\nSolves the primal shallow water equations for a given primal_swe_problem and bathymetry, returning the solution U, time points t, and spatial points x.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"}]
